==[[Etymology]]==
:Comes from Greek ''amethystos'' meaning "not drunken". The Greeks believed that the amethyst prevented intoxication.
==[[Noun]]==
#A transparent purple variety of [[quartz]], used as a [[gemstone]].
#A [[purple]] [[colour]].
